nodes.text: A female individual was the chieftess of the planet Inusagi. She owned a palace in the capital city of the planet. In 6 BBY, she was pressured into signing a treaty making her planet subject to the Galactic Empire. She was killed when Saw Gerrera's partisans crashed the sakoola blossom festival, where the treaty was being celebrated, and massacred all of the guests, Imperial and Inusagian alike.
